      <title>伯克希尔（Berkshire</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-17/berkshire-raises-stakes-in-japan-s-largest-trading-houses</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伯克希尔·海瑟薇公司（Berkshire Hathaway Inc.）增加了其在日本最大的贸易公司中的股份，这一举动有望为更广泛的东京股市提供支持。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-17/berkshire-raises-stakes-in-japan-s-largest-trading-houses</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Mar 2025 06:51:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>肯尼亚放弃了8亿美元的IMF评论，寻求新计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-17/kenya-seeks-new-imf-program-after-failing-to-secure-800-million</link>
      <description><![CDATA[肯尼亚同意不对现有设施的最终审查进行最终审查后，要求国际货币基金一项新的资金计划，该设施将解锁8亿美元。东非国家的纽带跌倒了。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-17/kenya-seeks-new-imf-program-after-failing-to-secure-800-million</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Mar 2025 06:20:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>资产经理提高欧元投注，因为对冲基金削减了短裤</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-17/asset-managers-boost-bullish-euro-bets-as-hedge-funds-cut-shorts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲对更大的财政支出的历史性枢纽促使资产经理将看涨的欧元头寸提高到五个月的高度，而对冲基金则押注了该货币的弱点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-17/asset-managers-boost-bullish-euro-bets-as-hedge-funds-cut-shorts</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Mar 2025 04:09:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
